  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 9961,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "生まれは小さな村だったが……10才になる頃には、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I was born in a small village... but by the time I turned 10,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9962,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "誰も近寄ろうとはしなかったそうだ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "no one would come near me."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9963,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "親でさえ、近づきたくても近づけない。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Even my parents couldn’t get close, even if they wanted to."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9964,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "自分でも制御する手段を知らず……というか、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I myself didn’t know how to control it... or rather,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9965,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "制御しようとせず。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I didn’t even try to control it."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9966,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "市販のアイテムで押さえ込むのも、限界があった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "There was a limit to suppressing it with commercial items."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9967,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "いくら魔法使い優遇のゼスって言ったって、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Even though Zeths favors magic users,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9968,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "いつ爆発するか分からんプチハニー爆弾を",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "no one had the tolerance to let a ticking little honey bomb explode at any time"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9969,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "好き勝手させられるほどの度量はない。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and behave however it wants."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9970,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "離れの納屋に住んで、飯だって怖々届けられるだけ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I lived in a separate shed, and even my meals were cautiously brought to me."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9971,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "まともな会話もできやしない。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I couldn’t even have a normal conversation."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9972,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "虐待の意図はなくとも、そうせざるを得なかった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Even though there was no intention of abuse, they were forced to act like that."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9973,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そうなると……子供の方だって、不安定になる。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Because of that... the child became unstable as well."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9974,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "感情が揺れれば、魔法の制御は更に難しくなる……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "If my emotions fluctuate, controlling my magic becomes even more difficult..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9975,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "14歳の時に、ついにでかい暴走を引き起こした。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "When I was 14, I finally caused a major rampage."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9976,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魔法災害の報を受けて、軍と共に向かったのが……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Upon hearing of the magical disaster, the military headed there along with..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9977,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "当時15歳、四天王になりたての千鶴子様だった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Chizuruko-sama, who was then 15 years old and newly appointed as one of the Four Heavenly Kings."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9978,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "遠距離から本人を仕留めて沈静化させよう……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "There was talk of taking her down from a distance to calm her down..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9979,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "て話もあったが、千鶴子様が却下。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "But Chizuruko-sama rejected that."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9980,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "結局、魔力をねじ伏せて押さえ込むことになった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "In the end, they had to subdue and suppress her magic power."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9981,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "軍の部隊、千人がかりくらいだったかなぁ……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "There was about a thousand soldiers from the military unit, I think..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9982,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "えらく苦労したよ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It was a tremendous struggle."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9983,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ああ、その場にいたんだ、俺。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Ah, I was there at the scene."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9984,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "何日か、魔力の押し合いを続けて……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "We struggled over magic power for several days..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9985,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "やっとこさ、向こうがぶっ倒れてくれた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Finally, she collapsed."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9986,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "千鶴子様が持ってきた、超強力な魔力抑制服を着せて",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "We put on the ultra-powerful magic suppressant suit that Chizuruko-sama brought"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9987,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ようやく安全に話せるようになった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and finally were able to speak safely."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9988,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はあ……やっと、大人しくしてくれたわね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Haa... finally, you’ve calmed down.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9989,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「アニス……危ないですか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Anis... is it dangerous?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9990,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「生きてるの…………だめ、ですか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I'm still alive... is that no good?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9991,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「まあ……危ないわね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well... it is dangerous.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9992,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「う…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ugh...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9993,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……だから、私の所に来なさい。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Therefore, come to me."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9994,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　私が制御の仕方、教えてあげる」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I will teach you how to control it.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9995,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「え…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Eh...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9996,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「すごいじゃない、あなた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Isn't it amazing, you?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9997,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　誰にもできない事ができるのよ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "You can do things no one else can.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9998,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9999,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「は、はいっ……！　あ、ありがとうございます！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Y-yes...! Th-thank you very much!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10000,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ええと……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Umm...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10001,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「名前？　千鶴子よ。山田千鶴子。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"My name? I'm Chizuruko. Chizuruko Yamada."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10002,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　名前で呼んでちょうだい」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Please call me by my first name.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10003,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はいっ――――千鶴子様！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Y-yes! Chizuruko-sama!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10004,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……大丈夫ですか？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Are you alright?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10005,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　正直、かなりヤバイと思いますが……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Honestly, I think it's pretty bad...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10006,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「常識を教え込めば、きっと平気よ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"If we teach her common sense, she'll surely be fine."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10007,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　村でもそういう教育、してなかったみたいだし。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It seems they didn’t provide that kind of education in the village either."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10008,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　きっとすごい魔法使いになるわ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "She'll definitely become an amazing magician.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10009,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それは…………確かにそうかも知れませんが」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well... that might indeed be true.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10010,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それに……ガンジー様なら、同じ事をするはずよ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Besides... if it were Ganji-sama, he would do the same thing.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10011,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「てな感じで……な」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Something like that... you know.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10012,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふ、ふおおおおおお……！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"F-fuoohhh...!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10013,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　なんと感動的な……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "How moving...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10014,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「千鶴子め……短絡的な真似を……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That Chizuruko... such a reckless act...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10015,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「は？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Huh?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10016,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そーなんだよなあ……千鶴子様も、周りも……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That’s right... both Chizuruko-sama and those around her..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10017,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　一般常識なんてすぐに身につくと思ったんだよ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "They thought common sense would be acquired quickly."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10018,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　初めは、な……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "At first, that is..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10019,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それが今でも、味方殺しのへっぽこ最強魔女か」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"And yet, even now, she’s still the hopeless strongest witch who kills her allies.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10020,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あぁ……千鶴子様かガンジー様辺りでないと、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yeah... if it weren’t for Chizuruko-sama or Ganji-sama around,"
    }
  ]
}

